      "content": "wait \"huge deflection\"? that seems a bit harsh lol. u basically just said that the people trying to hold bigots accountable are actually the ones stifling growth. isn't that kind of ignoring the actual damage bigotry does in favor of protecting the feelings of the people saying it? it feels like u might be taking a side here.",
